pedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}, {\"begin\": 312, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"British dressage starCharlotte Dujardinwithdrewfrom theParis Olympicson Tuesday after a video emerged showing her making \\\"an error of judgement\\\" during a coaching session.\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 431, \"end\": 447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section  Dujardin, a three-time Olympic champion and joint most decorated British woman Olympian, said she had withdrawn from all competition while authorities investigated the incident.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 764, \"end\": 771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9996221143442892, \"rank\": 0.0002559600398920566, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999450343821024, \"rank\": 5.4968639405035774e-05, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A video has emerged from four years ago which shows me making an error of judgement during a coaching session,\\\" she said in a statement, days before the Games.\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 1038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not immediately clear what the video showed.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Understandably, the International Federation for Equestrian Sports (FEI) is investigating and I have made the decision to withdraw from all competition - including the Paris Olympics - while this process takes place.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1162, \"end\": 1165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2075995883048142e-37, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What happened was completely out of character and does not reflect how I train my horses or coach my pupils, however there is no excuse.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am deeply ashamed and should have set a better example in that moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Charlotte Dujardin was eliminated from the European Championships in 2019 after blood was found on her horse, Mount St John Freestyle, in a post-competition check.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}, {\"begin\": 1568, \"end\": 1590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \